<Body><Title>四川攀枝花6.1级地震已造成38人死亡982人受伤</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008-09-03 16:08:29</ReportTime>　　
<Content>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">中国网</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">9月3日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">报道</Denoter></Event></Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s2">记者</Participant>从中国地震局<Denoter  type="stateChange" did="d2">获悉</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e3"><Time type="timeInterval" tid="t3">截至9月3日8时</Time>，发生在<Location lid="l3">四川攀枝花仁和区和凉山州会理县交界处</Location>的6.1级<Denoter type="emergency" did="d3">地震</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e4">已造成<Participant oid="o4">38人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d4">死亡</Denoter></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e5"><Time type="absTime" tid="t5">北京时间2008年8月30日16时30分</Time>，在<Location lid="l5">四川省攀枝花市仁和区与凉山彝族自治州会理县交界地区</Location>（北纬26.2度,东经101.9度）发生里氏6.1级<Denoter type="emergency" did="d5">地震</Denoter>。</Event>
			</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e6"><Location lid="l6">四川省攀枝花市</Location>、<Location lid="l6">凉山州</Location>，<Location lid="l6">云南省楚雄州</Location>、<Location lid="l6">昆明市</Location>等地有强烈<Denoter type="emergency" did="d6">震感</Denoter>。</Event>
			</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e7"><Time type="timeInterval" tid="t7">截至9月3日8时</Time>，<Denoter type="emergency" did="d7">地震</Denoter></Event>已造成
			<Event eid="e8"><Participant oid="o8">38人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d8">死亡</Denoter></Event>（其中四川32人，云南6人），
			<Event eid="e9"><Participant oid="o9">1人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">失踪</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e10"><Participant oid="o10">982人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d10">受伤</Denoter></Event>（其中四川637人，云南345人）。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e11"><Location lid="l11">四川省凉山彝族自治州会理县</Location><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d11">死亡</Denoter><Participant oid="o11">27人</Participant></Event>，
			<Event eid="e12"><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d12">失踪</Denoter><Participant oid="o12">1人</Participant></Event>；
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e13"><Location lid="l13">攀枝花市</Location><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d13">死亡</Denoter><Participant oid="o13">5人</Participant></Event>（东区1人，西区2人，仁和区1人，米易县1人）；
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e14"><Location lid="l14">云南省楚雄彝族自治州元谋县</Location>和<Location lid="l14">永仁县</Location>分别<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d14">死亡</Denoter><Participant oid="o14">5人</Participant>和<Participant oid="o14">1人</Participant></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>经初步调查，
			<Event eid="e15"><Denoter type="emergency" did="d15">地震</Denoter></Event>主要造成
			<Event eid="e16"><Location lid="l16">四川省攀枝花市东区</Location>、<Location lid="l16">西区</Location>、<Location lid="l16">仁和区</Location>、<Location lid="l16">米易县</Location>、<Location lid="l16">盐边县</Location>和<Location lid="l16">凉山彝族自治州会理县</Location>等6个县（区）72个乡镇，<Location lid="l16">云南省楚雄彝族自治州元谋县</Location>、<Location lid="l16">永仁县</Location>、<Location lid="l16">武定县</Location>等3个县20个乡镇<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d16">受灾</Denoter></Event>，灾区总人口约120万。
			</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			极灾区烈度达到Ⅷ度。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			其中Ⅷ度面积约600平方公里，Ⅶ度区面积约1500平方公里，Ⅵ度区面积约7500平方公里，灾区总面积约9600平方公里。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			另外
			<Event eid="e17"><Location lid="l17">楚雄州大姚县</Location>、<Location lid="l17">牟定县</Location>、<Location lid="l17">昆明市禄劝县</Location>和<Location lid="l16">丽江市华坪县</Location>等地区遭受到一定<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d17">破坏</Denoter></Event>。
			</Sentence> 
			(本文来源：中国网 作者：陈维松)
